Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:04.98,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Index has committed 103,000 grimoires to memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:07.52,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to defeat the magician,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:09.07,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,but Index's wounds are severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:12.40,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It seems her wounds can be treated with magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:15.36,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,but the students in this city are all unable to use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.90,0:00:19.20,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So, basically, Komoe-sensei, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.39,0:00:25.77,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,500)\pos(1158,493)}#03 Necessarius\NThe Church of Necessary Evil
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.65,0:00:26.19,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What is the current local time... in Japan Standard Time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:28.96,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,And the date, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:32.74,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,July 20th, 8:30 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:36.79,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I notice you did not consult a clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:39.18,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Is that time accurate?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:42.83,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a clock in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:47.73,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei's internal clock goes by the second, so that should be accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:54.11,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,I can adjust my internal body clock with a stable diet and exercise pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:57.90,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,From the position of the stars and the angle of the moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.90,0:01:02.06,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,...it matches the direction of Sirius with an error of 0.038...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.90,0:01:04.49,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Then, to confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.80,0:01:10.73,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The current local time in Japan Standard Time\Nis July 20th, 8:30 pm, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:15.33,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we're at the 53 second mark, to be exact.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.11,0:01:18.32,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, you shouldn't get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:20.37,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry, regeneration is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:35.65,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The end of Cancer, the period is midnight between 8 to 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:37.03,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Bearing is to the West.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:38.96,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The guardian of Undine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.96,0:01:40.81,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The angel is Helheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.11,0:01:42.69,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,What's... that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.69,0:01:43.50,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:48.48,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I will need to borrow your hand and body from this part on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:51.35,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,If you follow my instructions,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:53.27,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,no misfortune shall befall anyone here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.27,0:01:55.23,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,and you shall have no need\Nto bear a grudge against anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.23,0:01:58.57,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Just lie down and wait for the ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.57,0:02:01.16,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... bandage... bandage...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:06.10,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Treatment of that level will not suffice in tending to my wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:08.53,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I do not understand the meaning of "ambulance",
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:11.82,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,but will that be able to completely tend to my wounds in the next few minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.82,0:02:16.86,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,...and replenish a sufficient amount of vital energy, mana, to my body?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.89,0:02:22.29,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.29,0:02:25.06,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei isn't a magical girl, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.24,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I am grateful for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:31.28,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,First...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:35.33,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,...what is that black object over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:40.20,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,This is a memory card for video games.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:44.36,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Please put that in the middle of the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:46.12,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mini-dining table, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:52.73,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a miniature model of this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:54.92,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The materials do not matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:56.88,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,If the shapes and roles fit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:58.19,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,then the ritual can be carried out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:07.93,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:09.77,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The location of your beer cans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:14.73,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I would be rather grateful if you followed my instructions accurately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:17.03,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,If you commit a mistake in the process,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:21.44,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,there is a possibility your nervous system will be burnt out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:27.95,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Failure entails the destruction and death of your body... is what I'm telling you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:31.42,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I will descend the angel and create a temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:34.04,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Repeat after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:11.21,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Link successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:13.54,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Link?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:17.84,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The temple created atop this table has been successfully linked to this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:21.38,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What happens in this room will also occur on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:25.42,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What happens on the table will also occur in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.02,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Please image it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:30.60,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:32.06,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,A golden angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:33.46,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Its physique is that of a child's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.93,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,It possesses two wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.93,0:04:36.87,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Image the sight of this beautiful angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:39.05,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:48.81,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Telling me to think of an angel out of the blue is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.88,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,We are not actually summoning an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:03.21,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,As the mage, you must use your will to create the form of an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:04.30,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:06.72,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,A cute angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.38,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,A cute angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.65,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,A cute angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:12.48,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,A cute angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:14.16,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,A cute angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:16.32,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,A cute angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:17.98,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,A cute angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:34.75,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I didn't really summon an angel... did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:40.42,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Fixation of the form has failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:45.24,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, a blue-colored Undine to protect the temple shall suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:46.95,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Let's proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:51.07,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,A cute angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:53.09,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,A cute angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:55.00,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,A cute angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.60,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,A cute angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:58.64,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,A cute angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:01.11,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,A cute angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:02.55,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,A cute angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:04.98,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,A cute angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:06.90,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,A cute angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:57.99,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Along with the replenishment of mana,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:07:00.35,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I have confirmed the avoidance of life endangerment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:02.38,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,John's Pen will now enter sleep mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:09.40,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:13.69,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,All that's needed to heal me is my own stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:16.39,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The wound itself has been treated, so I will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:21.36,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God that he doesn't need to shoulder this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:23.44,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Shoulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.95,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,If I had died here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:29.03,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,he might have needed to shoulder this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:34.60,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,You were worried about Kamijyo-chan more than yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:38.93,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:42.29,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.23,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,...but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:56.60,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And why is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:08:01.16,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...that the big beer drinker and smoker, the mature Komoe-sensei's, pajamas...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:03.49,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...fit you perfectly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:06.42,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's like, how many years apart are you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.04,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Don't snub me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}PLACEHOLDER
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:14.43,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I do feel that my chest feels restricted in these pajamas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:10.93,Default-alt,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,*nod* *nod*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:13.43,Default-alt,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,*nod* *nod*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:17.44,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your comment is insulting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.30,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:20.84,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.55,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:25.00,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,I am an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.68,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Kamijyo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:31.13,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimately, who is this girl to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:33.43,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,My sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:36.94,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when you shouldn't be lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:40.10,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,She's a beautiful foreign girl with silver hair and blue eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:36.94,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Sorry! I really mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:40.10,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I lied! Sorry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:40.95,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijyo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:46.13,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, can I ask something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:47.43,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Desu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:53.47,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Are you asking this to tell\Nthe executive board of Academy City?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:54.30,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Desu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:58.83,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what kind of trouble you two are in,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:01.60,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,but whatever it is, since it took place inside the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:03.63,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,it is a teacher's job to take care of the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:05.05,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,It is an adult's duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:11.68,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,If I know that you two are treading on dangerous ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:14.89,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,I am not stupid enough to just stand by and do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:19.10,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If you were a complete stranger,\NI wouldn't hesitate at all in involving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.95,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But I owe you a favor, Sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.37,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't want to get you involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:29.51,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Saying something cool like that and trying to cover things up will not make Sensei forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:32.03,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where're you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:35.53,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,This is a suspension of negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:38.81,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei will now go to the supermarket to buy materials to make breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:44.74,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,In the meantime, Kamijyo-chan, you think about how and what you should tell me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:45.77,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:47.10,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:52.04,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,When Sensei gets into shopping too much, she might forget about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:57.85,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,When she gets back, Kamijyo-chan, you shouldn't try to play tricks and should just tell her first thing, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:19.27,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,She's a wonderful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:22.06,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, Komoe-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:22.66,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.66,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get Sensei any deeper into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:29.42,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we cannot let her use any more magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:33.08,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Grimoires are dangerous things,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:37.34,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,with the contrasting common wisdom and the altered laws written in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:42.93,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,A "different world" like that is poisonous for "this world", regardless of good and evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:44.24,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Poisonous?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:47.71,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Without mentioning magicians,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:51.45,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,if people of "this world" come in touch with knowledge of a "different world",
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:54.02,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,their brains will be destroyed just because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:55.30,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.64,0:10:58.14,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what magic is like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:10:59.36,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:03.91,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really want to know the burden I am carrying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:09.27,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:12.08,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I'm the Father now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:17.30,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you truly are like a Father listening to a confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.82,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The Christians were originally all united as one,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:25.92,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,but why do you think they have split up\Ninto so many different churches?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:29.91,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:32.76,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Because they brought politics into religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:37.39,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,They split, opposed each other,\Nand chose various paths of their own...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:40.07,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,...even though they all believed in the same God...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:45.06,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,All of them have evolved in their own way and gained their own "personality".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:46.41,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Personality, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:49.37,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The English Purist Church that I belong to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:54.09,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Since England is a country of magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:56.13,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,witch hunts and inquisitions,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:12:00.19,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,this kind of anti-magician culture\Ndeveloped in extraordinary manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:04.46,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,That is why the English Purist Church has a special division.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:08.67,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,In order to defeat magicians, this division has researched magic and devised strategies against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:11.44,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,It is called the church of necessary evil, "Necessarius".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:12.87,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Necessarius?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:16.74,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,But, in order to understand an impure enemy, our own hearts will become impure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:19.38,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Coming in contact with an impure enemy, our body will become impure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.90,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,It is a division that gathers all the impurities in one spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:24.38,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,And the greatest impurity of all is-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:28.26,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Those 103,000 grimoires...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:28.93,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:32.84,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Magic is like a formula.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:34.88,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,If one can successfully reverse engineer it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:37.76,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,one can even neutralize an adversary's attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:40.24,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,If one knows all the magic in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:43.36,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,one will be able to neutralize all the magic in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:46.01,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,So the 103,000 grimoires were-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:48.26,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,-hammered into your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:52.47,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If these were really that dangerous,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:54.30,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,they should've just burned 'em and not bothered reading 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:58.01,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What's important isn't the book itself but the content.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:12:59.38,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the original is destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:02.16,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,it would be meaningless if it were passed down through oral tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:04.79,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, humans are unable to destroy the originals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:08.61,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The human mind is unable to, to be exact.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:13.39,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,They had no choice but to seal them off because they couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:19.09,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, people are after the bomb implanted inside your head, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:26.67,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,With these 103,000 grimoires, one can absolutely be able to distort the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:30.01,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:34.49,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you keep all this to yourself this whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:38.49,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:40.21,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,And I didn't want to scare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:41.84,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,And... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:45.03,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want you to hate me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:47.43,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.82,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You're dissing me right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:51.85,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Church of necessary evil, Necessarius?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:53.83,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,103,000 grimoires?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:55.85,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It really does sound like bullshit,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.54,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,and hearing all this would be really hard for someone to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:13:59.30,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:01.68,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:07.42,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:10.55,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you memorized 103,000 books,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:12.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,do you think I'd consider you disgusting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:16.32,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Have some faith in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:18.73,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be judging people on your own, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:32.73,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,See? I've got my right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:34.50,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Magicians are no match for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:38.70,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,But, you said you needed to go to school for extra lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:40.37,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:41.88,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,You definitely did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:46.44,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,F-Forget school!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:50.01,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you say you had to go to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:52.05,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,That you had plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:55.37,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,My presence made you feel uncomfortable, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:56.78,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Uncomfortable, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:09.36,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,How's Index?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:11.01,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,She's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:15.14,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I've researched the background of the teenager accompanying her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:18.29,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's up with his right hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:23.03,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,To say the least, he is not a magician or even a supernatural power user.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:24.34,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:27.72,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to tell me he's just a normal high-schooler?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:30.71,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:37.23,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,This world wasn't created easy enough for some amateur with no powers to be able to dispatch Innocentius.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:38.86,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,That is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:45.22,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, the problem is his battle abilities actually belong in the category of "worthless students that like to pick fights".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:49.57,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps there is an intentional blackout on his information?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:53.61,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,And Index's wounds were actually healed through magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:59.61,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki, do other magic societies exist in this Far East?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:02.40,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,If they were moving inside this Academy City,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:05.08,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,some should at least be detected by the institution's antennae.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.37,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy forces are unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:10.29,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,We have no backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:12.23,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,She seems really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:15.68,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,She really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:18.64,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,She's been leading a happy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:24.41,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer do we have to keep tearing and ripping that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:26.38,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a perplexing emotion for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:28.90,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,You, who have been in that place in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.69,0:16:32.51,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:37.80,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, when Komoe-sensei came back from the supermarket,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:42.01,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,she didn't ask anything and let us stay in her apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:44.96,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she forgot all of it while she was doing her shopping,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:47.93,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,or maybe she decided to forget everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:49.89,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,At least, I didn't ask her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:54.20,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Bath-tub! Bath-tub!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:56.37,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Bath-tub~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:58.48,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Bath-tub! Bath-tub!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:00.51,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Bath-tub~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:08.56,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma! Touma! Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:10.63,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:14.18,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of fun to call someone's name without any purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:15.32,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:17.39,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:19.98,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Komoe mentioned that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:22.36,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,In a Japanese public bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:24.75,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,there's this thing called coffee milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:25.79,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:27.17,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,and this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:30.08,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,put your hand on your hip and drink it like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.60,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What's this coffee milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:36.34,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Is it like cappuccino?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:39.34,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing elegant like that in a public bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:42.58,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You may experience a culture shock when you see the large bath, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:45.83,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,They've got nothing but narrow bathtubs in England, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:49.82,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I actually don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:50.57,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:54.21,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Because, I was in Japan before I realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:57.07,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure about anything in England.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:01.03,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you speak Japanese so fluently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:03.77,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:09.20,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I was born in London and apparently was brought up inside St. George's Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:13.55,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I came here about a year ago, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:15.05,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:17.96,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, because my memories keep disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:24.14,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,When I first awakened, I didn't even know who I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:27.21,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even recall what I ate the night before,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:30.61,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,but I knew about magicians, Index, Necessarius...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:33.29,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,...knowledge like that kept popping up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:34.86,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I was really scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:40.16,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So, you don't even know why you're losing your memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:41.66,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:47.99,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:49.31,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Are you angry or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:51.98,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Am not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:54.81,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I might apologize if I offended you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:56.73,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,but what is angering you, Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:57.91,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Going through puberty?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:19:03.42,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear "puberty" from someone with a pedo body like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:05.47,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, what's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:08.09,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,You are angry from what I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:09.52,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:12.48,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,That you're pretending to be angry to tease me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:15.33,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I think I don't like that aspect of you, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.33,0:19:16.61,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:18.22,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even like me to begin with,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:20.66,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,so don't be saying stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:26.12,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how desperate I am, I don't anticipate such romantic events filled with love comments from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:29.37,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:32.92,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you being quiet and staring angrily at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:33.92,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,My princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:36.30,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:40.05,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.57,0:19:48.90,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:52.02,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Biting me all she wants\Nand going on her own way like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:58.31,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:07.79,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,There's... no one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:11.79,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a rune.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:17.45,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,A rune that removed all people from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:19.42,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:23.58,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki Kaori is my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:27.93,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:27.94,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The other magician, Kanzaki Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.94,0:20:29.86,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one that slashed Index?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:33.00,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,How can she do things like this with indifference?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:35.53,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Perfect Memorization".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.53,0:20:37.49,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross paths,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.49,0:20:38.92,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,this epic will begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
